  "title": "VETERINARIAN FULL TIME",
  "description": "<p>Full-Time Veterinarian</p><p>We are looking for an experienced and passionate Full-Time Veterinarian to join our established and progressive veterinary practice.</p><p>💼 Position Overview</p><p>This role offers an excellent opportunity for a veterinarian who values clinical excellence, professional growth, and a supportive team environment.</p><p>💰 Remuneration & Benefits</p><p>* Basic salary: $8,000 per month</p><p>* Commission: Up to 6%, based on performance<br /><br />* Attractive overall earning potential of up to $14000<br /></p><p>* 5 Day weekday  shift possible . NO WEEKEND WORK</p><p>* Supportive team and well-equipped clinic</p><p>🩺 Key Responsibilities</p><p>* Deliver high-quality medical and surgical care to companion animals</p><p>* Conduct thorough consultations and diagnostic assessments</p><p>* Build trusted relationships with clients through clear and compassionate communication</p><p>* Collaborate effectively with veterinarians, nurses, and support staff</p><p>* Uphold the highest standards of clinical practice and ethics</p><p>🎓 Requirements</p><p>* Registered veterinarian in Singapore</p><p>* Relevant veterinary qualifications and clinical experience</p><p>* Strong communication and interpersonal skills</p><p>* Commitment to excellence in veterinary care</p><p>🌟 Why Join Us</p><p>* Competitive and transparent remuneration structure</p><p>* Positive, professional, and collaborative work culture</p><p>* Opportunities for continuous learning and career development</p><p>* Modern facilities and advanced equipment</p><p>📩 Application</p><p>Interested candidates are invited to submit their CV to:<br />manager@ivc.com.sg</p>",
